# AbxrLib for Unity - Meta Quest QR Code Scanner Development Rules

## ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Keep This File Updated

**BEFORE starting any new approach to fix the passthrough camera:**
1. Read this entire file to understand what has been tried
2. Check the "What Failed" section - DO NOT repeat those approaches
3. Review the "Current Status" section to see what's in progress

**AFTER attempting any new approach:**
1. **IMMEDIATELY update this file** with the results:
